{"tid":808464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同女神打羽毛球柒到想窿捐!","createTime":"2018-09-06T10:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:59.000Z","uid":119688,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"04007cd3a5f1ef98664b4b4da837e9efcc4f41c6","tid":808464,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"我自己就無做開運動<br />\n約到女神咪試下打下囉<br />\n<br />\n懶型買左塊唔知咩牌子<br />\n成2千幾 好似比人當水魚咁劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇人打得多 見人地撿波用塊拍new上黎<br />\n以為好撚易啦 仆街我越new個波越走<br />\n最後仲成塊拍趺埋<br />\n<br />\n咁岩女神係對面飲完水返黎<br />\n果刻真係柒到想窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後打完佢地就無再約我 <br />\n唔知咩事 明明都算打得幾開心<br />\n死啦 塊拍咁貴玩左一次就要封塵 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d8ca3bf230b7aee26fe38803ef68839dbdbc64","tid":808464,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"無是咁的重作"},{"pid":"39dd29766b04501506b036f34932bef1183b223e","tid":808464,"uid":119688,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b6d8ca3bf230b7aee26fe38803ef68839dbdbc64","tid":808464,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"無是咁的重作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"你老母噴白帶啦 <br />\n真人真事 3個鐘頭前"},{"pid":"55029f7ba4593629a25cc51addab365c0bc1b6f5","tid":808464,"uid":22566,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"椰汁炸豬扒"},{"pid":"6a613d3e91e523e92fec7753e5027ac299f88f09","tid":808464,"uid":198400,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"39dd29766b04501506b036f34932bef1183b223e","tid":808464,"uid":119688,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b6d8ca3bf230b7aee26fe38803ef68839dbdbc64","tid":808464,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10